Andrew Eskilsson <mpt95aes@pt.hk-r.se> writes:

> Suddenly zsh started to have problems with history-editing,
> sometimes it works, sometimes I have problems like:

Hmm, the symptoms sound a lot like you've gotten into vi editing mode,
while being used to emacs mode.  Have you perhaps changed your EDITOR
or VISUAL variable to vi?  Perhaps you should try putting a
"bindkey -e" in your .zshrc.

Hope this helps.

Bas.

